All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CameraAlreadyCaughtActivity
    This activity is displayed when the user scans a QR code that has already been caught.
    CameraAnalyzeScannedActivity
    This activity analyzes a scanned camera and determines whether it has already been caught by the user or if it's a new camera to be added to the user's collection.
    CameraCaughtNewActivity
    The activity for displaying and confirming a QR code that has been scanned using the device camera.
    CameraScanActivity
    Activity that uses the device's camera to scan barcodes and QR codes.
    CodeRefOpenStreetMapActivity
    Represents an activity that displays a map using OpenStreetMap and allows for displaying the user's location, as well as adding overlays like a scale bar and compass.
    Comment
    This class represents a comment object containing the details of a comment made by a user on a code.
    CommentDB
    CommentDB is a class which handles all comments for Comment object.
    CommentList
    CommentList is a class which maintains a list of comments and operations associated with them
    CustomListForCustomAdapter
    Adapter (customized) for linking/showing the backend-datalist (of objects) with the UI-content-list (in content.xml)
    CustomListScoreBoard
    The CustomListScoreBoard class extends ArrayAdapter of type Player to display a custom list of Players on a scoreboard.
    DBConnection
    Connects to Database, gettings the users unique firestore ID to identify them.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    LocationTrack
    The LocationTrack class is used to track the user's location using the device's GPS and network providers.
    NavBarAdapter  
    OnCompleteListener<T>
    Interface used to handle result of DB operation.
    OpenStreetMapActivity
    The OpenStreetMapActivity class is an activity that displays a map using osmdroid library.
    PhotoTakeActivity
    Responsible for capturing an image from the camera and detecting any barcodes or QR codes in the image.
    PhotoViewActivity
    Activity for displaying a photo taken with a QR code.
    Player
    This class represents a Player who competes to scan and own more valuable QRCodes than other Players in the application.
    PlayerController  
    PlayerDB
    PlayerDB is a class which handles all database operations for Player objects.
    ProfileActivity
    This class represents the activity where the user can view their profile information.
    QRCode
    This class represents a QRCode scanned by Players in the application.
    QRCodeDB
    QRCodeDB is a class which handles all database operations for QRCode objects.
    QRCodeImageViewActivity
    The QRCodeImageViewActivity displays the image and information of a QRCode.
    QRCodeLibraryActivity
    The QRCodeLibraryActivity is responsible for displaying a list of QR codes in the user's library.
    QRCodeViewActivity
    QRCodeViewActivity is an Activity class that displays details of a QRCode and provides options to delete, view image, go back to the library, and navigate to the home screen.
    QuickNavActivity
    The QuickNavActivity class is responsible for handling the main navigation screen in the app.
    QuickNavNewActivity  
    ScoreboardActivity
    ScoreboardActivity is an activity class that displays a list of players and their scores in a scoreboard.
    ShowIndividualCodes
    ShowIndividualCodes is responsible for showing the details of each QRCode
    SignUpActivity  
    StoreNamePoints
    StoreNamePoints is an object class responsible for storing the details of a QRCode
    TitleActivity
